// The canonical OMG ShapesDemo type, as spoken by RTI Connext, Eclipse
// CycloneDDS, eProsima Fast DDS and ZeroDDS on the standard `Square` /
// `Triangle` / `Circle` topics.
//
// Extensibility is **@final** on purpose: that is the wire form every classic
// ShapesDemo client uses, and the only extensibility that interoperates with a
// non-XTypes-negotiating peer. (CycloneDDS's IDL compiler also defaults to
// @final; Fast DDS's `topic_instances` example chose @appendable, which is why
// this suite regenerates it — see `fastdds/README.md`.)
@extensibility(FINAL)
struct ShapeType {
    @key string color;
    long x;
    long y;
    long shapesize;
};
